thread.title: Mike

author: Mike
title: Mike
text: Used to be my go to site for Saab parts. Last two orders were messed up. Needed a part ASAP. Part was "in stock" so I ordered and paid an additonal $38 for overnight shipping. Part arrived 4 days later and was not shipped until 2 days after purchase, from another supplier. Second part I ordered took over a week to get here because, once again, part was not in stock even though the site said they had 3 in stock. Prices are not the lowest around so it was a no brainer to shop elsewhere from now on...
